                    <span>cut and pasted from a wide variety of sources, this book's words and images have the look and feel of high school project. I admire the author's intention but the result is an unfortunate mish-mash. There's even a quote attributed to KATHERINE Hepburn.<BR>Not recommended.</span>
                  
